Title: My favorite moment in succession is the end of season 2 when they're getting on the boat and Tom ask...
Author: Jake Koenig
Summary: My favorite moment in succession is the end of season 2 when they're getting on the boat and Tom asks "Why are we here again?" because: 1. How did he fly to a boat in greece w/o knowing why? 2. Every ep is an event that doesn't make sense with guests that shouldn't be there.
